+
+**`solveToggle`** (src/index.ts:16-138): Solves the binary toggle puzzle over GF(2). For underdetermined systems with free variables, uses either direct enumeration (≤20 free vars) or meet-in-the-middle (>20 free vars) to find the minimum button presses.
